":issue:`1515`.)"

#: ../../whatsnew/2.7.rst:1174
msgid ""
"The :mod:`ctypes` module now always converts ``None`` to a C ``NULL`` "
"pointer for arguments declared as pointers.  (Changed by Thomas Heller; "
":issue:`4606`.)  The underlying `libffi library "
